comment.raw:
/**
 * This component can embed a Cloudinary video the Cloudinary Video Player.
 *
 * @example
 *
 * Simple Video Example
 * ```svelte
 * <script>
 * 	import { CldVideoPlayer } from 'svelte-cloudinary';
 * </script>
 *
 * <CldVideoPlayer width="1920" height="1080" src="videos/mountain-stars" />
 * ```
 *
 * @see
 *
 * https://svelte.cloudinary.dev/components/video-player
 */
comment.summary: This component can embed a Cloudinary video the Cloudinary Video Player.

examples.name: Simple Video Example
examples.content:
```svelte
<script>
	import { CldVideoPlayer } from 'svelte-cloudinary';
</script>

<CldVideoPlayer width="1920" height="1080" src="videos/mountain-stars" />
```
